data.description: Welcome home to this bright 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home. On the upper level, there are 3 bedrooms, a full bath, and a spacious living room, along with your dining room and kitchen. The lower level has a large family room along with a 4th, large bedroom. Work from home? There is an office space on the lower level as well. Just walking distance from Lake Pulaski and local parks. A great place to call home!
